    {
      "id": 164238,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "The OIDC JWT token issued on a new Sign in with Apple ID to the Cloudflare Dashboard had an excessive lifetime. When intercepted by a malicious actor, it enabled impersonation of the affected user on multiple devices during the entire token validity period without the need to re-authenticate.\nThe issue was fixed by the engineering team and the lifetime of the generated JWT was significantly decreased.",
